    <idx><h>nesting</h></idx>
    <idx><h>loop</h><h>nested</h></idx>
That code won't work until we put cards in the array.
One way to populate the array is to write nested <c>for</c> loops:
</p>

<program xml:id="arrays-objects_arrays-cards-4">
