<p>
Since <c>cards</c> has type <c>Card[]</c>, pronounced <q>card array</q>, an element of <c>cards</c> has type <c>Card</c>.
So <c>println</c> invokes the <c>toString</c> function in the <c>Card</c> class.
</p>

